{
  "page": "Chain",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Company\" title=\"Golden Company\"><img alt=\"Golden Company.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/43/Golden_Company.svg/50px-Golden_Company.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/43/Golden_Company.svg/75px-Golden_Company.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/43/Golden_Company.svg/100px-Golden_Company.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Serjeant</span><br />Chain</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Company\" title=\"Golden Company\"><img alt=\"Golden Company.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/43/Golden_Company.svg/50px-Golden_Company.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/43/Golden_Company.svg/75px-Golden_Company.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/43/Golden_Company.svg/100px-Golden_Company.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Chains_TheMico.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Chains TheMico.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f7/Chains_TheMico.jpg/250px-Chains_TheMico.jpg\" width=\"250\" height=\"354\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f7/Chains_TheMico.jpg/375px-Chains_TheMico.jpg 1.5x, /images/f/f7/Chains_TheMico.jpg 2x\" /></a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nChains<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Titles</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Serjeant\" title=\"Serjeant\">Serjeant</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Ser\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ser\">Ser</a> <small>(allegedly)</small></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Company\" title=\"Golden Company\">Golden Company</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Free_Cities\" title=\"Free Cities\">Free Cities</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Mother</th><td>\nA <a href=\"/index.php/Prostitution\" title=\"Prostitution\">camp follower</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (appendix)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i> (appears)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Chain</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Sellsword\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Sellsword\">sellsword</a> and a <a href=\"/index.php/Serjeant\" title=\"Serjeant\">serjeant</a> in service to the <a href=\"/index.php/Golden_Company\" title=\"Golden Company\">Golden Company</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ar2_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ar2-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> His given name is unknown.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance_and_Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance and Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#The_Winds_of_Winter\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>The Winds of Winter</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance_and_Character\">Appearance and Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Chain&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance and Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>As a <a href=\"/index.php/Serjeant\" title=\"Serjeant\">serjeant</a>, Chain is a high-ranking officer.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> He claims to be a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a>. A brusque man, Chain is taller than <a href=\"/index.php/Young_John_Mudd\" title=\"Young John Mudd\">Young John Mudd</a>, and wears two rusted chains across his chest. Instead of a blade, he uses five feet of heavy linked <a href=\"/index.php/Iron\" title=\"Iron\">iron</a> as a whip.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ar2_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ar2-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Chain&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Chain's great-grandsire had fought for <a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_I_Blackfyre\" title=\"Daemon I Blackfyre\">Daemon I Blackfyre</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_of_the_Redgrass_Field\" title=\"Battle of the Redgrass Field\">Battle of the Redgrass Field</a> and fled to exile across the <a href=\"/index.php/Narrow_sea\" title=\"Narrow sea\">narrow sea</a> with <a href=\"/index.php/Bittersteel\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bittersteel\">Bittersteel</a>. His father was a sellsword of the Company, and fathered Chain on a <a href=\"/index.php/Camp_follower\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Camp follower\">camp follower</a>. He was raised to speak the <a href=\"/index.php/Common_Tongue\" title=\"Common Tongue\">Common Tongue</a> and think of himself as <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westerosi</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ar2_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ar2-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Chain&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Chain&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Chain, like the rest of the company, swears his allegiance to <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_Targaryen_(son_of_Rhaegar)\" title=\"Aegon Targaryen (son of Rhaegar)\">Aegon Targaryen</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Volon_Therys\" title=\"Volon Therys\">Volon Therys</a> before they <a href=\"/index.php/Landing_of_the_Golden_Company\" title=\"Landing of the Golden Company\">invade Westeros</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"The_Winds_of_Winter\"><i>The Winds of Winter</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Chain&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: The Winds of Winter\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<table style=\"margin: 4px 10%; border: 1px solid #aaa; background:#fbfbfb;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"padding: 2px 0 2px 0.5em;border-left: 10px solid #f28500;\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\"><img alt=\"Content.png\" src=\"/images/c/cc/Content.png\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" />\n</div></td><td style=\"border: none; padding: 0.25em 0.9em; width: 100%;\"> <b>Warning</b> <br /> This information has thus far been released in a sample chapter for <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>, and might therefore not be in finalized form. Keep in mind that the content as described below is still subject to change.</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>Chain and <a href=\"/index.php/Young_John_Mudd\" title=\"Young John Mudd\">Young John Mudd</a> hold <a href=\"/index.php/Mistwood\" title=\"Mistwood\">Mistwood</a> for the Golden Company. They keep Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Mary_Mertyns\" title=\"Mary Mertyns\">Mary Mertyns</a> under house arrest and host <a href=\"/index.php/Arianne_Martell\" title=\"Arianne Martell\">Arianne Martell</a>'s party for a night.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ar2_2-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ar2-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>While escorting Arianne part of the way to <a href=\"/index.php/Griffin%27s_Roost\" title=\"Griffin&#39;s Roost\">Griffin's Roost</a>, Chain reveals the story of his family, and tells her he had never set foot in <a href=\"/index.php/Westeros\" title=\"Westeros\">Westeros</a> before the invasion. He also reveals some details about his fellow sellswords, including <a href=\"/index.php/Young_John_Mudd\" title=\"Young John Mudd\">Young John Mudd</a>'s skill with <a href=\"/index.php/Dice\" title=\"Dice\">dice</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Two_Swords\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Two Swords\">Two Swords</a>' fondness for red haired women, <a href=\"/index.php/Little_Pussy\" title=\"Little Pussy\">Little Pussy</a> and his lucky <a href=\"/index.php/Cat\" title=\"Cat\">cat</a>, the time someone stole <a href=\"/index.php/Harry_Strickland\" title=\"Harry Strickland\">Harry Strickland</a>'s favorite <a href=\"/index.php/Elephant\" title=\"Elephant\">elephant</a>, and other stories of the members of the Golden Company. He also slips that Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Connington\" title=\"Jon Connington\">Jon Connington</a> is planning to seize <a href=\"/index.php/Storm%27s_End\" title=\"Storm&#39;s End\">Storm's End</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ar2_2-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ar2-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Chain&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Appendix\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Appendix\">Appendix</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ar2-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ar2_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ar2_2-1\">2.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ar2_2-2\">2.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ar2_2-3\">2.3</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ar2_2-4\">2.4</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Winds_of_Winter\" title=\"The Winds of Winter\">The Winds of Winter</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/Arianne_II_(The_Winds_of_Winter)\" title=\"Arianne II (The Winds of Winter)\">Arianne II</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd24.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_24\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 24\">Chapter 24</a>, The Lost Lord.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403123336\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.082 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.269 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 699/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10909/1000000\nPost‐expand inclu